Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Our tech-savvy E-GO Collection of bags lets you safely carry all your "tech-accessories" and look terrific doing it! With the Tablet Messenger you're off and running with all your lifestyle essentials safely protected in this stylish cross-body messenger bag. Featuring top quality, weather-resistant, all leather construction this bag is designed with strategic protection for your electronic essentials. Padded compartments for laptop, tablet, reader or similar devices and interior compartments to protect smart phone and music player means you will always have exactly what you need. A top zipper closure quickly and easily secures electronics and personal belongings. An inside zipper pocket is perfect for a passport and personal items and an outside zipper pocket is for quick access items. The bag is designed with a fold-over top flap for added security. Great additional features like a key keeper and convenient ID tag and Protective cloth storage bag give additional protection and usability. An adjustable leather cross-body strap offers a convenient and comfortable carrying solution. What fits inside: Up to 10-Inch laptop computer and 1 tablet device or reader. Or many combinations of smaller items including laptop, reader and compact camera plus a wallet, keys, make-up, hair brush, hand sanitizer, tin of mints all your lifestyle essentials.
